Letters can also be written in vertical:

`python main.py write --word hello --foreground fire --background white_large_square --border --border-emoji ATM_sign --vertical`

outputs
```
🏧🏧🏧🏧🏧🏧🏧🏧🏧
🏧⬜⬜⬜⬜⬜⬜⬜🏧
